A final-year political science student of the University of Benin (UNIBEN), in Edo State, Augustine Izu, was reportedly shot dead on Tuesday after his final examination. It was learnt that four armed men, wearing masks, invaded his house in Ugbowo, Edo State and killed him. UNIBEN main gate. His friend, Walter Emeka who was also shot in the arm, was taken to the hospital. It was reported on November 2, 2019 how a student of the same university identified as Africicanado was shot dead during the Faculty of Social Sciences Final Year Jean Carnival by a rival cult group.